Module tagtraum.audioplayer4j
Package com.tagtraum.audioplayer4j.macos

Class AVFoundationPlayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tagtraum.audioplayer4j.macos.AVFoundationPlayer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AudioPlayer, AutoCloseable
    public class AVFoundationPlayer
extends Object
implements AudioPlayer
    Natively-backed audio player for macOS. Property changes like time, duration, and uri can be listened to via PropertyChangeListeners, playback events are accessible via AudioPlayerListeners.
    Author:
    Hendrik Schreiber

        public int getMinTimeEventDifference()
        Description copied from interface: AudioPlayer
        Minimum delay in ms between "time" property events. This is not necessarily a precise, binding value. Instead, it is treated by the implementing player class as a non-binding user-wish.
        Specified by:
